{"tid":2030573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"24/5 想聽到民族重光 香港獨立","createTime":"2020-05-22T23:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T00:43:02.000Z","uid":68982,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a9a1ce282fd7a2edae067cdd552b13e99f63ba","tid":2030573,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:26:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民族重光 香港獨立<br />\n</span></span><br />\n覺得用民族重光比較獨特同貼切<br />\n<br />\n一直都得講緊係黑暗中黎明來臨就係重光，加上係極權壓迫下，民族唔只要自強更需要推倒極權重燃希望。<br />\n<br />\n再可以呼應<span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒巴理念: 攬炒，唔係Burnism，係 Phoenixism，係鳳凰重生 嘅必經過程。香港人，再無同中共妥協嘅空間。<br />\n但願從此人人覺醒，再無大眾、本土、泛民之分。<br />\n但願我地告別犬儒，告別投降，告別內鬥，從此只有重光派，為煲底之約奮戰。</span><br />\n<br />\n參考隔離post投票仲可以配合黃黑旗，黃色代表民族，黑色代表香港獨立，最後上黃下黑合併可以理解做黑暗中黎明來臨等於重光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VvOPcKS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVvOPcKS.png&h=6a0cbc9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1426a781d731166b86fef0a216619ca32daeea0","tid":2030573,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:28:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民族重光 香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"558a1345a0487c288590c64f6ac7efcb9e8da0ca","tid":2030573,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:29:03.000Z","msg":"或者「民族自強、光復香港」啦，因為總有淺黃同中華膠唔想獨立，但我地可以先民族自強建立認同，而光復香港就本身中性，但又可以暗喻獨立"},{"pid":"0d7ca04d18f0d14843259f1ae9ffce566fc18f6e","tid":2030573,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:29:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民族重光 香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b13fe98e645c70e75c86580a6834e5acafddb3a","tid":2030573,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T23:29:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民族重光 香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"c